N prove6 v0.0.1 ..'prove for Perl6'
M tags perl perl6 testing

O   -v  --verbose        .."Print all test lines."
O   -l  --lib            .."Add 'lib' to the path for your tests (-Ilib)."
O       --shuffle        .."Run the tests in random order."
O       --ignore-exit    .."Ignore exit status from test scripts."
O       --reverse        .."Run the tests in reverse order."
O   -q  --quiet          .."Suppress some test output while running tests."
O   -Q  --QUIET          .."Only print summary results."
O       --timer          .."Print elapsed time after each test."
O       --trap           .."Trap Ctrl-C and print summary on interrupt."
O       --help           .."Display this help"
O       --version        .."Display the version"

# Options that take arguments:
#
#     -I,  --incdir          Library paths to include.
#     -e,  --exec            Interpreter to run the tests ('' for compiled
#                            tests.)
